{"tid":1243572,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[少甜] 珍貴手錶失而復得有感","createTime":"2019-06-19T13:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T00:01:02.000Z","uid":263631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29b5460ac356669e7499f7702ec5c3d0c3f15e5a","tid":1243572,"uid":263631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"我係一個普通平凡既連仔，平時獨到冇朋友，打飛機都係一個人，鐘意自己同自己捉棋多過同人出街。有一日，我覺得其實毒L一個唔開心，於是就諗住去運動場跑步，睇下有冇機會識到另一半，唔洗再自己一個吃火鍋。<br />\n<br />\n落到場就梗係係側邊拉下筋，順便望下今日有冇咩獵物。好快就見到一個幾合眼緣，於是靜雞雞跟住佢後面跑。因為本身天生有啲運動基因，至少唔會好似啲肥仔大肚腩咁跑到喘晒氣，我一個箭步輕輕就跑過左佢，然後回頭一個冷笑，我相信我已經得到左一個毒L唔應該有既自信。仔細望佢雙眼，見到一種似笑非笑既眼神，究竟佢係睇穿左我對佢既心思，定係佢知我根本只係外強中乾，跑多兩圈就會精(力) 盡人亡？係我諗到入晒神既時候，我已經見到佢既身影係我側邊閃過。一種既屈辱感由心而出，激發左我潛藏左廿年既爆發力。<br />\n<br />\n大戰左15回合(圈),  我同佢都筋疲力竭，佢伸出左佢既右手，好似係想同我握手言和，表達&quot;不如大家唔好再鬥落去&quot;既意思，我心諗我而家攰到好似射左十次咁，仲邊有力再跑，於是我伸出我既左手，輕輕咁握住佢既右手，突然間我個心&quot;拍拍拍&quot;咁跳，跳到就黎跌出黎，係毒L以前從來未有過既感覺。係果刻我好驚，驚到即刻縮手，頭也不回咁衝左入更衣室，諗住俾自己同細佬都有時間冷靜下。下意識摸一摸下面，弊，冇左既？我隻手下面隻手腕上面隻錶唔見左! 我諗番頭先好似除左隻錶放左係場側邊，心諗幾舊水夠食十幾餐M記，於是我唔理細佬既情況，衝番出去搵，但已經見唔到佢地既蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n當我好失望咁返返更衣室既時候，我見番我隻手錶，上面留左張紙仔，而且有電話號碼係上面，呢種珍貴手錶失而復得既感覺好複雜。咁多位巴絲，究竟我應唔應該add佢wts呢？"},{"pid":"479a779a80b5e519b6008041ab3961a4d7441adc","tid":1243572,"uid":113360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻錶除咗係側邊<br />\n佢又點知係你嘅<br />\n你以為佢係你嘅獵物<br />\n可能其實你先係佢嘅獵物"},{"pid":"59e972c43585397f147199450fa8dfcbb7f451b6","tid":1243572,"uid":202231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"Add!!!"},{"pid":"da2a11446da151b0ba9f68471438a368698ccfde","tid":1243572,"uid":263631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59e972c43585397f147199450fa8dfcbb7f451b6","tid":1243572,"uid":202231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"Add!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:59:29.000Z","msg":"好怕羞，咁大個仔第一次"},{"pid":"689667c1200e98a92751e165e25af5971e6c6210","tid":1243572,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"原來係講故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1ea679ac57bfc1ffd9b83a73a6e88cd133ce4e","tid":1243572,"uid":263631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689667c1200e98a92751e165e25af5971e6c6210","tid":1243572,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"原來係講故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"多謝忠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7dedeba31b9377824d4e18e3a403fdb2713117","tid":1243572,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"隻錶會員唔會係日本業餘工藝師既手作"},{"pid":"009cc6ed09608324578e8f1830b7cc46a5ef424a","tid":1243572,"uid":263631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7dedeba31b9377824d4e18e3a403fdb2713117","tid":1243572,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"隻錶會員唔會係日本業餘工藝師既手作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fFeqzw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfFeqzw8.jpg&h=90155b9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係呢隻囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢隻兩餐M記都食唔到"},{"pid":"1656ecf33e1c62a0cfee3adc96eb46a6a023dec9","tid":1243572,"uid":202231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"咁仲有冇下文？"},{"pid":"4001150690a535062b4456c7c2393e4b3a4b899f","tid":1243572,"uid":263631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1656ecf33e1c62a0cfee3adc96eb46a6a023dec9","tid":1243572,"uid":202231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"咁仲有冇下文？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"如果佢應我機就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71023e8c21362f2b93928ac0a911cdaf3ce63db6","tid":1243572,"uid":113360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4001150690a535062b4456c7c2393e4b3a4b899f","tid":1243572,"uid":263631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1656ecf33e1c62a0cfee3adc96eb46a6a023dec9","tid":1243572,"uid":202231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"咁仲有冇下文？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"如果佢應我機就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:22:01.000Z","msg":"推到有下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650ffc254b6fc06d77569f29675d06fbb76de065","tid":1243572,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0823acfcba9437676e3fd214f4769e22b643921","tid":1243572,"uid":263631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"電話wts聲一響，係佢覆我<br />\n<br />\n話說尋晚講到係運動場入面，有個人(以下簡稱S)  執到我隻手錶，上面仲留低左有佢電話號碼既字條。多謝連登巴絲既鼓勵，我終於send左個msg俾佢。老豆由細到大都講，得人思果千年記，人地幫左你點都要多謝番人，於是我就膽粗粗打左&quot;3q&quot;俾佢，諗住表達我最崇高既謝意。<br />\n<br />\nS: 今晚？<br />\n<br />\n我一臉迷茫，乜唔係尋晚發生既事咩？點解寫今晚？咦~, 唔通佢想今晚同我食飯？<br />\n<br />\nS: 3q好貴喎<br />\n<br />\n我load左一陣，咦~，原來佢讚緊我既謝意如同黃金咁貴重，果一刻好想多謝我呀爸，原來佢教既野真係無錯，真誠係會有人睇到。<br />\n<br />\n我： 今晚可以啊，但我冇咩錢請你，不如平啲？<br />\n<br />\n心諗我返intern已經窮到燶，最多請佢食兩個豬柳強都係22個大洋，希望佢唔好介意。<br />\n<br />\nS: 好啦，見係你就平啲啦，不過你帶袋。今晚運動場等<br />\n<br />\n今晚應唔應該去運動場見佢？我又應該拎幾大個袋去呢？距離放工仲有4小時，有冇巴絲可以解答下我。"},{"pid":"e59ce1df3dce0dfbab9cd31794922a91a10aa625","tid":1243572,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8c4a65c118d090517de480f7a5b6f7e88b9514","tid":1243572,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />["}]}